Decrepit Paddock
You stand inside of a grazing paddock just outside of the barn. To your shock, you discover dozens of animal skeletons inside the paddock. Cows, pigs, goats, all of them look to have been forgotten here and left for dead. Who could have let this happen?

The large barn looms to the East and the field to the West.

> east

> east

Old Barn North
The interior of the barn is massive and has not been maintained over the years, as it is missing boards along its walls. It won't be long until the roof collapses.

Next to you near the entryway; you see a pile of miscellaneous sporting goods. There is a large workbench across from you along the wall near the stables. You can travel deeper into the barn by going South.

> Take Tackle Box

> Take Tackle Box
You pick it up.
> south

> south

Old Barn South
You find yourself facing a wall of old cobblestone. Here, the barn is in as bad of shape as it is to the North. The wooden boards are weathered, warped, and discolored from years of exposure to the elements. Antique farming tools hang from hooks on the walls.

You can see Wooden Ladder.
