> north

Hidden Room
This tight space could have been a closet at some point, but now it is more reminiscent of a small jail cell. The wooden wall panels are warped and have mostly come untacked. There is a small desk in the corner of the room, and a dirty cot lay next to you.

You can exit the room to the South.

