Swampy Pond
You come up to a small pond in the middle of the forest. Earlier in the year, the bog would be alive with the croaking of toads and frogs, but October has chilled them all into hibernation, and the swamp lay eerily silent. Fog rolls atop the surface of the green, slimy water as you scan your flashlight back and forth. You wonder; could there be fish in here?

You can head back South the way you came.

> use fishing net on pond

> use fishing net on pond
You throw the fishing net out into the pond and slowly drag it towards the shore. You discover a human Skull inside the net. You take the Skull.
