Darkened Field
This larger field looks like it once was used to grow corn or possibly soybeans, but now it is covered in tall grass. An old Farmall tractor sits in the center of the field. Barely visible through the fog, you see the shadow of a farmhouse to the North, a decrepit barn to the East, and a treeline to the Northwest.

