Front Porch
You stand in front of an abandoned farmhouse. It is an old construction, possibly dating back to the '20s or '30s. The siding is greyed, and the paint has all but peeled away, suggesting that it has not been occupied for many years. On the porch; you see a broken porch swing, some empty planters, and a rocking chair.

The front door is directly North of you. You notice a second-story window just above the doorway.

