Downstairs Hallway West
This narrow hallway is covered in cobwebs, and you watch dust particles floating in and out of your light's beam as you scan the area. Pictures are hanging along the northern wall, and several boarded-up windows are on the southern wall.

The hallway continues East, or you can enter the living room to the North.

